stark electric jesus is a 2014 short film inspired by the poem prochondo boidyutik chhutar or stark electric jesus written by malay roy choudhury .   the film has won the official selection as the only indian film at the trinidad and tobago film festivalin new media section and has been selected for screening at leeds independent film festival .   the film has also won 27 official selection in 20 different countries and also won ' best video art ' from poland , ' most promising artist ' award from madatac ,06 , spain and ' best fantasy film ' award from hrizantema international horror & fantasy film festival , serbia .